{"tid":2445192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民眾人權日上街　軍方再實彈掃射　多人死亡　據報死者包括僧侶","createTime":"2021-03-13T12:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T13:43:52.000Z","uid":227445,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"564f1ac97b295559a2adad6dd5681e6264874b60","tid":2445192,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://external.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQE50cY526S9EadP&amp;w=500&amp;h=261&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FMYANMAR-Link_Fi3Rv_1200x630cropcenter.png&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_cb=1&amp;_nc_hash=AQEguaL-rJhGLIAd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQE50cY526S9EadP%26w%3D500%26h%3D261%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.thestandnews.com%252Fmedia%252Fphotos%252Fcache%252FMYANMAR-Link_Fi3Rv_1200x630cropcenter.png%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_cb%3D1%26_nc_hash%3DAQEguaL-rJhGLIAd&h=68df0f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2021 年 3 月 13 日，緬甸軍方實彈掃射民眾，多人傷亡。（Photo by STR/AFP via Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n緬甸反政變步入第 40 日，今日（13 日）是緬甸「8888 民主運動」死者的死忌，也被視為當地的人權日，各地民眾號召上街示威，但再遭警方開火鎮壓。根據《路透社》報導，目前至少 5 人死亡，包括一名 19 歲海事大學新生 Htet Myat Aung；當地媒體 Myanmar Now 指，一名受傷僧侶剛死亡，令死亡數字再增加。《路透社》東南亞編輯指，即使愈來愈多人因上街流血，示威仍然持續。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/GettyImages-1231680507-1_sQRno_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FGettyImages-1231680507-1_sQRno_1200x0.jpg&h=6c0b8673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2021 年 3 月 13 日，緬甸示威者以「Black bloc」衣著出席仰光的反政變集會，並舉起三指手勢。(Photo by STR/AFP via Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwV4r9FVkAETJ-m?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwV4r9FVkAETJ-m%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=d0ecd33a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天原是「8888 民主運動」死者 Phone Maw 的死忌，後被全民盟及民運人士提倡為緬甸人權日。根據《路透社》，當地示威者昨晚於仰光舉行紀念燭光晚會，同時有示威者集合於警局外要求釋放被捕人士，再遭警方開火鎮壓，兩人凌晨中槍死亡。<br />\n<br />\n紀念示威行動持續至今天，《路透社》指，仰光、曼德勒及勃固至少有 5 人死亡，其中兩人於曼德勒靜坐行動中被槍殺，當場死亡，另外一人為 19 歲海事大學新生 Htet Myat Aung。網上傳出 Aung 生前及遺體的照片，包括其學校參與運動等照片，他今日於勃固腹部中槍不治。<br />\n<br />\n從相片可見，多人受重傷入院，甚至手指斷開；Twitter 亦有照片顯示，有男生口部中槍爆開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwWGaQlU8AUaJDh?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwWGaQlU8AUaJDh%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=47b78473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwWGaQjUUAMFwEU?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwWGaQjUUAMFwEU%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=28b3661c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwWGaQlUYAEcYbV?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwWGaQlUYAEcYbV%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=1918afbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwWGjIYVIAMziE1?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwWGjIYVIAMziE1%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=78816c9c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拜燈 我個拜燈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe74d8bb8b506669ca0f18efa9a809f57d867c1","tid":2445192,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"戀童登：有冇幼幼先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458df406acc9